sequenceDiagram
  actor Patient
  participant Pharmacist
  participant Web as PWA + Web Worker
  participant RT as OpenAI Realtime STT
  participant API as Application API
  participant LLM as OpenAI Responses

  Patient->>Pharmacist: Symptom, question, or medication concern
  alt Typed keywords
    Pharmacist->>Web: Enter short phrase
  else Push-to-talk
    Pharmacist->>Web: Hold microphone control
    Web->>RT: WebRTC audio stream
    RT-->>Web: Partial transcript deltas
  end
  Web->>Web: Normalize, extract slots, detect negation
  Web->>Web: Critical red-flag gate
  Web->>Web: Exact/rule/BM25 retrieval
  Web-->>Pharmacist: Instant say-now card
  opt Ambiguous or wording refinement requested
    Web->>API: Redacted slots + card IDs + sequence
    API->>LLM: store:false, strict schema, streamed request
    LLM-->>API: Structured update
    API-->>Web: SSE refinement
    Web->>Web: Drop if sequence is stale
    Web-->>Pharmacist: Refined card without replacing a frozen card
  end
  Pharmacist->>Web: Accept, override, or ask next question
  Web->>API: Coded feedback only
